data.pageContent:
Buy the best dog food online from Pet Circle with our best price guarantee and the convenience of fast, free delivery* direct to your door.

The right dog food = a happy, healthy doggo

Feeding your dog a quality food tailored to their size, lifestage and specific health needs is one simple thing you can do every day to invest in your dog's long term health. Good quality dog and puppy foods are precisely balanced to ensure they meet all of your dog's nutritional needs and are packed with extra beneficial nutrients like omega fatty acids, antioxidants and prebiotic fibres.

Feed wet and dry dog food for optimal health

Mixed feeding, or feeding both dry dog food and wet dog food allows you to combine the convenience and economy of bulk bags of dry food with the variety and added health benefits of canned or pouch format recipes. Adding in a daily wet food meal offers your pooch new and exciting tastes and textures to enjoy, plus it also helps to increase water intake which in turn supports hydration and urinary tract health. You can also add extra nutrition to your pup by offering food toppers, supplements and treats

Nourish their inner carnivore with grain free, biologically appropriate and raw

Prefer a natural approach to nutrition? Natural, biologically appropriate and grain free dog foods from top reviewed brands like Black Hawk, Instinctive Bite, Orijen, Meals for Mutts and Ivory Coat focus on keeping it simple with recipes that team quality meat proteins with thoughtfully chosen fruits, vegetables and other natural ingredients which provide beneficial nutrients. Balanced Life, K9 Natural and Ziwi dog foods provide the ultimate in convenient raw feeding with their freeze dried or air dried recipes.
